                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10184" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2568</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">233 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大士茶亭：商业模式韧性</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Thanksgiving Tea: Business Model Resilience</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李永发，秦若曦，张蕾，方星蕊，林清廉，付训，杜林虎</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京茶亭文化传播有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业模式韧性；即时电商；视频号矩阵；价值创造；价值捕获</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business Model Resilience, Instant E-commerce, Video Account Matrix, Value Creation, Value Capture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创办于2014年的南京本土品牌“大士茶亭”，在新冠疫情冲击下，遭遇了客流锐减与经营成本高居不下的双重困境。2022年，大士茶亭主动关闭四家门店，将资源集中于一家门店，探索“茶馆+灵活创业”与“场景化体验”相结合的新模式。在此基础上，企业通过构建“即时电商+云店矩阵”销售通路以及试点“销售合伙人”制度，重塑价值创造与价值捕获方式。2025年，大士茶亭实现单店营收超五店总和，视频号累计成交订单超8000单，退货率接近零。本案例聚焦大士茶亭商业模式韧性的底层逻辑和实践做法，揭示企业在内外部环境变化中寻求跨经济周期可持续成长的机制与路径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Founded in 2014, Thanksgiving Tea, a local brand in Nanjing, has suffered from the dual dilemma of sharp reduction in customer flow and high operating costs under the impact of COVID-19. In 2022, Thanksgiving Tea took the initiative to close four stores and concentrated its resources on one store to explore a new model combining &quot;tea house + flexible entrepreneurship&quot; with &quot;scenario-based experience&quot;. On this basis, the enterprise reshaped the way of value creation and value capture by building the sales channel of &quot;instant e-commerce + cloud store matrix&quot; and piloting the &quot;sales partner&quot; system. In 2025, the revenue of Thanksgiving Tea will exceed the sum of five stores, the cumulative transaction orders of video number will exceed 8,000, and the return rate will be close to zero. This case focuses on the underlying logic and practice of the resilience of the business model of Thanksgiving Tea, revealing the mechanism and path of the enterprise to seek sustainable growth across the economic cycle in the change of internal and external environment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《营销管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值主张；价值创造；价值捕获；商业模式韧性</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
